WEBVTT

00:00:00.840 --> 00:00:02.040
Good evening.

00:00:02.600 --> 00:00:04.576
My journey to this stage

00:00:04.600 --> 00:00:06.216
began when I came to America

00:00:06.240 --> 00:00:08.080
at the age of 17.

00:00:09.240 --> 00:00:12.656
You see, I'm one
of the 84 million Americans

00:00:12.680 --> 00:00:13.976
who are immigrants

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:16.416
or children of immigrants.

00:00:16.440 --> 00:00:20.256
Each of us has a dream when we come here,

00:00:20.280 --> 00:00:23.296
a dream that usually has to be rewritten

00:00:23.320 --> 00:00:25.640
and always has to be repurposed.

00:00:26.560 --> 00:00:28.456
I was one of the lucky ones.

00:00:28.480 --> 00:00:32.296
My revised dream
led me to the work I do today: